# Vault Setup

## Install Vault

1. Download the Vault binary from the official HashiCorp website:
```sh
curl -O https://releases.hashicorp.com/vault/<version>/vault_<version>_linux_amd64.zip
```
2. Download the environment variable files:

- [allvars.live](http://_vscodecontentref_/2)
- [allvars.nonlive](http://_vscodecontentref_/3)

3. Source the non-live environment variables:

source ~/Downloads/allvars.nonlive

Verify the environment variables are set correctly:

```sh
set | grep VAULT
```

